<div class="bg-white text-center border-bottom border-2 p-4">
  <div class="container p-0">
    <div class=" font-weight-light">
      <p class="h3">
        Unlock your job offers potential today
      </p>
      <div class="lead">
        We evaluate and help you understand your job offers
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="p-3 text-center" style="background-color:#E33C20">
  <a href="https://www.producthunt.com/posts/offerkarma?utm_source=badge-featured&utm_medium=badge&utm_souce=badge-offerkarma" target="_blank"><img src="https://api.producthunt.com/widgets/embed-image/v1/featured.svg?post_id=150711&theme=light" alt="OfferKarma - Receive feedback on job offers | Product Hunt Embed" style="width: 250px; height: 54px;" width="250px" height="54px" /></a>
</div>

<div class="text-center border-bottom p-4">
  <div class="container p-0">

    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-md-6 p-2 p-lg-3">
        <div class="card-shadow rounded bg-white p-4 height-100">
          <h6 class="mb-3">
            <span class="fa fa-money-bill text-success mr-1"></span> Job offer evaluation
          </h6>
          <p class="text-muted font-weight-light">
            You need to be compensated fairly and we'll help you make sure of it by reviewing carefully every parts of your compensation breakdown and letting you know where you get low-balled.
          </p>
          <a href="/offers/new" title="" class="btn btn-success">Evaluate your offer</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 p-2 p-lg-3">
        <div class="card-shadow rounded bg-white p-4 height-100">
          <h6 class="mb-3">
            <span class="fa fa-users text-warning mr-1"></span> Referrals
          </h6>
          <p class="text-muted font-weight-light">
            Is your dream company ignoring your application? We think everybody deserves a chance to get an interview and we'll be happy to refer you whenever possible.
          </p>
          <a href="/referrals/new" title="" class="btn btn-success">Ask for a referral</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-light p-3 border-bottom">
  <div class="container p-2">
    <div class="h4 text-center">Recent offers submitted</div>

    <div class="row">
      <% @pending_offers.each do |offer| %>
        <%= render partial: "offers/offer_list_item", locals: { offer: offer } %>
      <% end %>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-3 text-center">
      <a href="<%= offers_path %>" class="btn btn-success">Explore <%= Offer.count  %> offers</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="p-3 border-bottom">
  <div class="container p-0">
    <div class="mb-2 text-center">Explore more offers from these companies</div>

    <div class="row">
      <% @companies.each do |company| %>
        <div class="col-4 col-xl-2 p-3 d-flex justify-content-center">
          <div class="d-flex justify-content-center mb-0">
            <a href="<%= company_path company.uuid %>">
              <div class="image-thumbnail-outer-lg d-flex">
                <img class="align-self-center image-thumbnail-lg p-3 p-md-2" src="<%= company.logo_url %>" alt="<%= company.display_name %> logo" title="<%= company.name %>">
              </div>
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      <% end %>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="bg-light text-center border-bottom p-4">
  <div class="container p-0">

    <div class="row row-eq-height">
      <div class="col-md-6 p-2 p-lg-3">
        <div class="card-shadow rounded bg-white p-4 height-100">
          <h6 class="mb-3">
            <span class="fa fa-chart-line text-danger mr-1"></span> Equity guide <span class="ml-2 badge badge-danger text-white">coming soon</span>
          </h6>
          <p class="text-muted font-weight-light">
            Equity is complicated. We'll help you ask the right questions so that you fully understand the value of your equity and the costs you might incur to own it.
          </p>
          <a href="/equity" title="" class="btn btn-outline-danger btn-sm">Learn more about equity</a>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-md-6 p-2 p-lg-3">
        <div class="card-shadow rounded bg-white p-4 height-100">
          <h6 class="mb-3">
            <span class="fa fa-handshake text-info mr-1"></span> Negotiation tips <span class="ml-2 badge badge-info text-white">coming soon</span>
          </h6>
          <p class="text-muted font-weight-light">
            The first offer a company makes is sometimes below your current market value. We think there is always room to negotiate and we'll help you through it.
          </p>
          <a href="/negotiate" title="" class="btn btn-outline-info btn-sm">How to negotiate</a>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>
</div>
